OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers,
OL,6,Fperhaps heavy and thundery, fading
OL,7,Fthrough the evening, with some brief
OL,8,Fclear spells likely. Low cloud, mist
OL,9,Fand some light rain or drizzle then
OL,10,Fspreading inland after midnight. Less
OL,11,Fcold than recent nights.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FCloudy start with outbreaks
OL,14,Fof light rain or drizzle for some,
OL,15,Fthese easing by the afternoon. Cooler
OL,16,Fthan recently, especially in the
OL,17,Feasterly breeze. Turning sunny from
OL,18,Fthe east later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
