OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith plenty of warm sunshine Wednesday
OL,7,Fand Thursday, but tempered by strong
OL,8,Feast to southeast breezes. Sunny
OL,9,Fspells and lighter winds Friday, but
OL,10,Fperhaps also showers.
